data.description: Round up the kids, pack up the car, and take a look at your new home! With 5 bedrooms (or 4 and an office), great family room, cozy fireplace, country sized kitchen, 2 car garage and another outback, all in the friendliest neighborhood...Minutes away from shopping, hospital, parks, and schools! This solid home with tongue and groove throughout, also features a one-year-old whole house, natural gas Generac generator, all new windows installed by Window World that come with a lifetime warranty, and enough space in and out for the whole family and all the toys! Book your showing soon because this one won't last long!
